summary: An ordinance accepting a deed from George Kinnear and wife, to the City of Seattle, to the following property to-wit: beginning at the Southwest corner of block 10, Kinnear 1st Rainier Beach Addition; thence south 50 feet; thence east parallel with and 50 feet south of the north line of Bangor Street (formerly Center Street) to the west line of lot 24, block 5, Kinnear 1st Rainier Beach Addition produced south; thence north along said line a distance of 50 feet; thence west along the north line of Bangor Street to a point beginning.
